Author: bluediner
Text: I took a bite of ice cream today earlier than I planned to eat it and basically had to talk myself down from the ED ledge that it wasn’t a binge. AND the ice cream wasn’t even actually vegan, although I thought it was so :( the whole thing sucked

Author: CiboChubChub
Text: This hits too close to home. My limit is 200-300, NEVER over 500, and even eating a 160 cal yogurt got me soooo nervous. Then when I had a burrito later I purged all of it and took a hour long bike ride.
